These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, zinnia, rose
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, spanish, turkish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, western, scientific
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is the russian##1
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who growsdahlia##7
11. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
12. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | rose    | azalea | zinnia    | dahlia   |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | russian | turkish |
| Movie-Genre           | epic       | western   | scientific  | comedy     |
| Beverage     | water      | milk   | hot-chocolate    | lemonade    |

