.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, onion, watermelon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, montecristo, aristoff, oliveros
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, traveling, writing, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, doctor, pilot, librarian
 1. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 3. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the pilot is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the doctor and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
10. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot   | onion       | watermelon    | mango      |
| Cigar   | siglo | oliveros | montecristo         | aristoff   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks   | baking  | traveling       | writing |
| Job         | engineer      | pilot  | librarian | doctor |

