City: hamburg, rome, liverpool, marseilles
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the bartender and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 3. the designer is the art-deco house##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
10. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
12. the palace house is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
