 6. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the person eating plum is the fan of salsa##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
11. the person eating apricot is not the fan of salsa##6

