 4. the person who likes blood-red is not the owner of the horse##6
 5. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is handball##7
10. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
11. the turkish is the owner of the rat##1
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person who likes white##7
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

