The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, badminton, weightlifting, cycling
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 7. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
10. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating spinach and the bluemaster-smoker##2
12. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |      4      |
