 3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
 6. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 7. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 8. the person playing whist is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
11. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the gothic-revival house is not the person playing canasta##6
14. the tower house is not the person eating onion##6
15. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person eating grapes##7

