 3. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
 4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 7. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to san-francisco##7
 8. the person who likes green is not the person traveling to hannover##6
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Color         | blood-red      | chestnut   | green   | purple       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Cigar   | siglo  | davidoff | oliveros   | swisher     |
| City         | hannover   | berlin    | san-francisco   | london |

