There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, black, light-blue, amber
 1. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 2. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who likes black is the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who likes blue##1
 9. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
12. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | singing      | hiking     | cooking   | baking    |
| Music-Genre     | punk | ambient   | jazz | gospel |
| City     | venice        | berlin     | edinburgh  | liverpool      |
| Color   | black       | amber | blue   | light-blue    |

 